ENERGY-SAVING & SOUNDPROOF - The thermal insulated curtains are thick enough to prevent energy-exchanging between indoor & outdoor, which means it could save your air conditioner fees no matter what in hot summer or cold weather. reviews.reviewText: For Christmas, I redid my daughter’s whole room and purchased these curtains. Came just as pictured and they look so good during the day light the stars light up the room

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My daughter absolutely loves these curtains. You can see the light through the stars. Keeps the room nice and dark at nighttime

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Gold & White Tasseled Corded Curtains: Affordable, Versatile, and Magical Enhancement to Any Room
reviews.reviewText: These curtains exceeded my expectations, especially considering the price point. The shading is entirely acceptable, ensuring they offer just the right balance between light filtering and privacy.The set includes two gold and white tasseled cords, adding a touch of sophistication. These cords can be used to tie back the entire panel or just the tulle, according to preference. Additionally, there are two elegant corded ties in a matching gold fabric. These details, coupled with the lovely rainbow of colors the curtains display, make them a stunning addition to any room.What's more, these curtains provide an opportunity to add a dash of magic to any room. Simply attach fairy lights to create a whimsical look that is sure to delight. They efficiently block out light and have become an adorable feature in my son's room.These curtains are especially striking during twilight hours, adding a serene and mystical atmosphere. They've made a perfect addition to our child's playroom. Their long, flowy design also works well in my daughter's room, adding a touch of elegance and charm. The adaptability of these curtains makes them a worthwhile purchase.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pretty-wish it came with 2 panels
reviews.reviewText: I was surprised how cute it looked, it's a little wrinkly due to the folded packaging but it's got a nice weight to it. It only came with one panel which is a bummer had to wait to complete the look. Otherwise super adorable looking.
